{
  "headline": "<h2>Gameplay and Rules</h2>",
  "content": "<p>Get ready to fish out some big wins with Catch of the Day Reeling ‘Em In! With a classic layout of 5 reels and 3 rows, this game has 10 fixed paylines where the minimum bet is only €0.20. That's cheaper than buying bait for an actual fishing trip! </p><p>But don't be fooled by the low minimum bet, the potential payouts are off the scales! Winning combinations are formed by landing at least 3 identical symbols on adjacent reels starting from the leftmost one. It's like catching a big fish - you never know when it's going to happen, but when it does, it's worth the wait! </p><p>And for all the left-handed players out there, rejoice! Reversing the button layout makes it possible to fish out wins with ease. Plus, activating Autoplay for automatic spins gives you the chance to kick back and relax while the game does the work for you. Just be sure to keep an eye on your balance so you don't end up with an empty hook! </p><p>Last but not least, the theoretical return to player is 94.52%. Not too shabby! If you're looking to get hooked on a new slot game, Catch of the Day Reeling ‘Em In is definitely worth a try.</p>"
}

