    "content": "<p>Catch of the Day Reeling ‘Em In has got your fishing rod ready for action and is here to offer you some exciting gameplay mechanics and features to hook you in. This classic layout keeps it simple with 5 reels and 3 rows which are packed with 10 fixed paylines, and you can bet a minimum of €0.20 per line. Landing at least 3 identical symbols on adjacent reels starting from the leftmost one is the trick to forming a winning combination. So, let’s hope it’s smooth sailing and you reel in the big one. If you’re lucky enough to land more than one winning combination on the same line, and feeling greedy, sorry, we meant lucky, only the highest value combo is paid, because life is all about making the hard choices, right? But hey, with the different amounts accumulated from winning combinations on different lines, you can have your cake and catch it too!</p>

